* The package consists of a client (thrulay) and a daemon (thrulayd).    *
* The thrulay client is usable immediately.                              *
*                                                                        *
* To run thrulayd from startup, add thrulayd_enable="YES"                *
* in your /etc/rc.conf                                                   *
*                                                                        *
